  "Description": {
    "English": "A memory is <span class=\"name name-stellar\">burned</span> into this strange material, an echo of another lifetime...<br><br>\"I came face-to-face with a creature more beautiful and bizarre than anything I have ever seen.<br>Despite no discernible eyes, I do not believe it is blind.<br>It was huge, glorious, serene. But then - with a flick of its tentacles, it was gone.<br>I have thought of nothing else since. I can only think of the whale. whale. whale. <span class=\"name name-special\">wail</span>.\"",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "记忆被<span class=\"name name-stellar\">烙进</span>了这种奇怪的材料，是另一个生命的回音......<br><br>“我面对面地遇到了一种我见过的最美丽且怪异的生物。<br>尽管不知道它们的眼睛在哪，可我认为它们肯定看得见。<br>它巨大、壮丽又安详，它的触手轻轻一抽，它便不见了。<br>从那以后，我再也无法思考其他事物。那头巨鲸在我的脑中萦绕不去。巨鲸，巨鲸......<span class=\"name name-special\">哀嚎</span>。“",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一段記憶<span class=\"name name-stellar\">已燒錄</span>進此奇異材料內，一段另一世的回音......<br><br>「我與一隻比我看過的所有事物都還要奇怪的生物面對面。<br>儘管辨識不出眼睛，我不認為牠沒有視覺。<br>牠很巨大、華麗、安詳。隨後......觸手彈了一下，牠不見了。<br>至此以後我什麼都沒想，只能想著鯨魚。鯨魚。鯨魚。<span class=\"name name-special\">哀號</span>。」"
  },
